# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Aetheris Backend - Environment Template
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values:
#   cp .env.example .env

# ── Application ──
PROJECT_NAME=Aetheris Enterprise Analytics
API_V1_STR=/api/v1

# ── Security ──
SECRET_KEY=<generate-a-strong-random-key>
ALGORITHM=HS256
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=120

# ── Seed Database Passwords (must meet length/complexity rules) ──
SEED_ADMIN_PASSWORD=AdminPass2026!
SEED_FINANCE_PASSWORD=FinancePass2026!
SEED_LOGISTICS_PASSWORD=LogisticsPass2026!
SEED_VIEWER_PASSWORD=ViewerPass2026!

# ── Database ──
# SQLite (local dev):
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./aetheris.db
# PostgreSQL (production):
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://<user>:<password>@<host>:5432/<dbname>

# ── SAP S/4HANA Integration ──
SAP_BASE_URL=https://your-sap-s4hana-host.com
SAP_CLIENT=100
SAP_USERNAME=<your-sap-user>
SAP_PASSWORD=<your-sap-password>
USE_MOCK_SAP=True

# ── Redis ──
# REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0
